        ],
        "blocks": [
            {
                "name": "Item",
                "type": "item",
                "settings": [
                    {
                        "type": "range",
                        "id": "img_scale",
                        "min": 100,
                        "max": 200,
                        "step": 1,
                        "default": 100,
                        "unit": "px",
                        "label": "Scale image"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "image_picker",
                        "id": "img",
                        "label": "Image"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "label": "Title",
                        "id": "title",
                        "default": "the skincare regime builder"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "range",
                        "id": "title_margin_top",
                        "min": 0,
                        "max": 80,
                        "step": 2,
                        "default": 0,
                        "unit": "px",
                        "label": "Title margin top"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "richtext",
                        "label": "Text",
                        "id": "text",
                        "default": "<p>The core product collection is your everyday routine and has been formulated to suite all skin types, eliminating the challenge of choosing the right products for your skin. The system is straightforward and has minimal steps, so you donâ€™t have to invest too much time looking after your skin but can have the confidence all bases</p>"
                    },
                    {
